name: leaning on wall
description: Let the people speak to you. Created by arthur (a teacher in Shanghai) & owae.ga (a multimedia artist from Switzerland) Photo is shot on a Rolleicord with Portra 400, video is created by owae.ga. The combination creates a personality, a character, for each of these photos that makes you contemplate what their experience is like and how they think. Find both artists on twitter @ryanartwalker and @owae_
